        <h3>Underground Havoc</h3>
        <p>This level is meant to be an underground level about 3/4ths through the game as a near-maze area. My main objective was to have an atmosphere of exploration, and set up some sort of mini-games along the way, such as the "avoid the Piranha Plants while climbing the vine" and "Get that 1-Up in the mini-pipe run."</p>
        <p><strong>In Hindsight</strong>: </p>
        <ul>
            <li>this level is way too long, and should be split into two separate, smaller levels.</li>
            <li>A few encounters are a little too unfair - specifically the bullet-bill part.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
