        <h3>Pipe Maze</h3>
        <p>Ever since playig World 7 in Super Mario Bros 3, I've loved the idea of a pipe maze level. This is my attempt at one.</p>
        <p><strong>In Hindsight</strong>: </p>
        <ul>
            <li>The underwater secret area is too long for being a side objective.</li>
            <li>The difficulty feels uneven. The second half of the level has far fewer enemies than the first half.</li>
            <li>The player has to play through the level more than once to get everything - something I'm not usually a fan of.</li>
